text.tspan: Human rights protection vs. liberal democracy, 2017
Human rights scores capture the extent to which citizens' physical integrity is protected, with higher scores meaning
more protection. Liberal democracy based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, ranging from 0 to 1
Source: Schnakenberg and Fariss (2014) and Fariss (2019), OWID based on V-Dem (v12)
